title: Opening Title Sequence | American Horror Stories - Episode 3: "Drive In" (HD Clip)
author: AHS Crave
comment: This is my favorite AHS opening so far! 🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤
This single intro ate up the entire opening credits budget for the rest of the season AND Double Feature
description: The third episode of American Horror Stories, titled "Drive In"— written by Manny Coto and directed by Eduardo Sánchez— stars Rhenzy Feliz (Chad), Madison Bailey (Kelley), Ben J. Pierce (Dee Dee), Naomi Grossman (Rabid Ruth), Leonardo Cecchi (Milo), Kyle Red Silverstein (Quinn), Amy Grabow (Tipper Gore), John Carroll Lynch (Larry Bitterman), Brandon Popo (Tillis), Courtney Hawkins (Ticket Taker), Stephanie Stanton (Reporter), Adrienne Barbeau (Verna), and Catherine Adell (Lanie). All rights belong to 20th Television, FX Networks, and Hulu.
